<h3>Intro</h3>

The services affected by this policy may need to process personal data to work properly.
<br>For clarification, the following questions shall be answered here.

<br><ul><li>Which categories of personal data are processed?</li>
<li>What is the purpose and the legal basis thereof?</li>
<li>What is the source and how long is data saved?</li>
<li>What are your rights?</li>
