<h3>Children under age 16</h3>

People below age 16 may use this work only with consent of their holder of parental responsibilities.
<br>Consent to the terms and conditions and the privacy policy must be given also by this person.
<br><br>

<h3>About links</h3>

In this work you will find links to content from third parties.
<br>We have examined those carefully, but as they can be updated dynamically we cannot account for inappropriate content.
<br>Should we become aware of such content, we will consequently delete those links. We gratefully take hints regarding this matter.
<br>These third parties define own terms and conditions and privacy policies, which are not connected to our services.
<br>Because those only apply after visiting the links, you then should carefully examine them as well.
<br><br>

<h3>Third party services</h3>

To fulfil our services optimally we implement third party services.
<br>Those are subject to their own terms and conditions and privacy policies which also apply and shall be linked here.

<br><br>Actively we do not implement third party services right now.
<br>We want to inform you however that on Download via e.g. the Google Play Store the respective terms and conditions and privacy policy apply.
<br>https://policies.google.com/terms/?hl=en
<br>https://policies.google.com/privacy/?hl=en
<br><br>

<h3>Which categories of personal data are processed?</h3>

We do not process personal data right now.
<br>For increased comfort the current selections may be saved locally.
<br>This is done via 'Preferences' in the folder /data of your device and overwrites itself.
<br>Also you may delete them anytime within the settings of your device.
<br>All information you may share within this work remain under your sovereignty.
<br>You are encouraged to always keep your device up-to-date and secure.
<br><br>
	    
<h3>What are your rights?</h3>

You have the right to request from the controller access to and rectification or erasure of personal data or restriction of processing concerning the data subject and to object to processing as well as the right to data portability.
<br>You have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority.
<br>Should you have given consent, you have the right to withdraw it.
<br><br>
		
